4678, "The Avenger cannon was completed by Terran and Vasudan scientists as a joint project following the end of the Terran-Vasudan War, and a rising number of encounters with the Shivans. This version uses photon acceleration technology to achieve the same effect - a good light cannon that is equally effective against shields and hull plating."

