4700, "EAW-32 Mace"

4701, "Tactical Kinetic Weapon"

4702, "A rapid tactical energy cannon, the Mace has limited destructive firepower, but a huge kinetic punch which can destabilise and deflect targets. This, in addition to its high refire rate and long range, makes it very useful for destroying fragile bombs before they reach their target. The Mace is often installed on EA Stentor interceptors to thwart bomber attacks on capital ships."

