4903, "EAM-209 Eviscerator"

4904, "A delivery unit that launches 30 smaller heat seeking swarm missiles forward in a twenty degree cone two seconds after launch, the Eviscerator showers targets with death. Usually installed on the Claymore Mk. II, this innovative device is far more effective than the ancient Synaptic cluster weapon it is based on. Fortunately the heat-seekers are fairly easy to throw off, but at close range this may be impossible."

