5103, "EAF Claymore Mark III"

5104, "The Mark III Claymore is a prototype medium fighter. It is a good all-round combatant which can carry most EA weaponry. In combat the Claymore III excels at destroying both medium and heavy fighters, and acts as a good point defense against bomber attacks."

