5107, "Atlantis Corp"

5108, "The brand new Stentor interceptor sets a new benchmark for high-performance flyers. Capable of outrunning any ship from the Great War, the Stentor is the pinnacle of Earth Alliance fighter technology. Recently arrived for the end of the Jovian campaign, this fighter will be integral in bringing the Sol conflict to a close."

