5181, "The new 'corvette' class of ship will provide us with a new tactical advantage never seen before. Bridging the gap between the maneuverable cruiser and the all-powerful destroyer, the corvette can be inserted into situations where either a cruiser or a destroyer would have an extreme disadvantage. Its Geodess missile system can attack any warship from extreme range and from almost any angle. Heavily shielded turrets on the Skotas will frustrate most attempts to disarm the corvette."

