5219, "The Belus is our sole freighter, replacing the Poseidon and Chronos freighters. Thanks to the necessities of inter-planetary combat, resupplying warships is usually unnecessary, and so the Belus is used for other purposes - namely the construction of Lycaon outposts along the Asteroid Belt."

